{"tid":916241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人自救","createTime":"2018-11-25T14:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T03:40:03.000Z","uid":192988,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"54490245c67adb367d711eda1ef6f0574c9859d9","tid":916241,"uid":192988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T14:39:17.000Z","msg":"依個petition 已經有一萬人簽左<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/223531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F223531&d=KuT%2Ftr4FTowZ5QrYLSFrBf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=42781755\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/223531</a><br />\n英國政府短期內要回應, 相信會係英國或國際社會有一定既noise. <br />\n<br />\n當中有好多五毛/hater 話英國社會無人支持, 其實唔係無道理. 而家有一萬人簽署係第一步.  <br />\n<br />\n我地應該趁著個勢, 將<br />\n1.\t香港現況話俾英國及國際社會知, 同埋解釋<br />\n2.\t我地唔係難民<br />\n3.\t香港人當年無得公投就俾返中共<br />\n4.\t香港人普遍有一定財富<br />\n<br />\n總之我地唔會好似中東難民咁擁去英國, 我地只想平權<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到可以<br />\n<br />\n1.\t將上面4點寫成文章, post /share 去英國既social media <br />\n2.\t整啲影片係youtube<br />\n3.\t在英港人幫手 spread<br />\n<br />\n就係要將個message spread 俾多啲人知.<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家集思廣益, 有力出力, social media 好重要. 當年就係一張相, 全球蔓延，促使國際反應, 歐洲人變為同情中東人<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%89%BE%E5%85%B0%C2%B7%E5%BA%93%E5%B0%94%E8%BF%AA%E4%B9%8B%E6%AD%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2589%25BE%25E5%2585%25B0%25C2%25B7%25E5%25BA%2593%25E5%25B0%2594%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%25AD%25BB&d=KuT%2Ftr4FTowZ5QrYLSFrBf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=32b6defb\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%89%BE%E5%85%B0%C2%B7%E5%BA%93%E5%B0%94%E8%BF%AA%E4%B9%8B%E6%AD%BB</a><br />\n<br />\n我地暫時唔需好似中東人冒死游水去歐洲, 但唔代表我地乜都唔做<br />\n<br />\n港人自救"},{"pid":"afddb4855eb9a3874517a7d0699b4882006995ef","tid":916241,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=